# ── PROJECT LAYER — never lives in the seed ──────────────────────────────────
# These directories belong to project forks. The seed has them empty (.gitkeep).
# Merging upstream/main into a project fork will NEVER touch these paths.

# In a project fork, all storage/ is yours to commit freely.
storage/*
!storage/.gitkeep
!storage/AGENTS.md
!storage/db/
!storage/db/**
!storage/progreso/
!storage/progreso/**
!storage/fork_doc/
!storage/fork_doc/**
!storage/docs/
!storage/docs/**

# Project-specific custom blocks built with AI
# Politica del FORK (2026-07-06): los bloques specialized SON capa fork y se trackean
# TODOS. La regla de ignore del seed creaba archivos invisibles para git y para los
# worktrees de lanes (misma trampa que storage/db, cerrada por goal/storage-dedup).
!src/components/specialized/
!src/components/specialized/**



# local Claude Code settings (machine-specific, never committed)
.claude/

.vercel
.env*.local
/.history/
.codex/

# backups del CLI agno: locales, no se versionan
storage/progreso/backups/
